{"about_the_game":"Cat Herders is a chaotic 1-4 player, split-screen coop game. It's about herding cats. Each level has a goal, and your job is to get the troublesome cats into that goal as quickly as possible using a variety of items!<br><br>We just pushed our big Anniversary Update which improves gameplay and the UI a whole bunch!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/xmas_gif_450.gif?t=1699324838\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/HERD!-1.png?t=1699324838\" /><br>Use items like tuna, your computer keyboard and Cat Snax\u2122 to draw cats towards the goal. Use scarier items like a barking robot dog to push them in whichever direction you please. Use more chill items like the music box to put them to sleep while you figure out a plan of attack. Use the cat trap to move multiple cats quickly. Create chaos with the cat cannon!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/COOPERATE!-1.png?t=1699324838\" /><br>Coordinate with your friends in 2-4 player split-screen (Steam Remote Play/Parsec friendly!) to get the cats to the goal as fast as you can. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/SET_RECORDS!-1.png?t=1699324838\" /><br>Compete to finish each level in the fastest time with gold, silver and bronze medal times. Compare your times to other cat herders on the online leaderboards!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/PLAY_FESTIVE_LEVELS!-1.png?t=1699324838\" /><br>Halloween and Christmas maps have been added! Herd cats in the abandoned medieval village while being hunted by the spoopy ghost cat or entice cats with presents in a beautiful winter wonderland.<br><br>","achievem